		<RichText x="739" y="223" width="384" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷法施放一个雷球，造成<span color="#ffacff">60%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#d24cff">强攻强化：</span><span>施放的雷球有弱追踪性。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="427" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷法施法，召唤一个雷环造成<span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害，雷环围绕自己，持续3s，接触造成</span><span color="#ffacff">80%</span><span>伤害。<br/></span><span color="#d24cff">强攻强化：</span><span>接触伤害提升至</span><span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，持续时间延长至6s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="438" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷法传送，出现在玩家正前方，同时造成<span color="#ffacff">100%</span><span>伤害，近处受玩家攻击时概率传送远离玩家，盾破之后持续攻击有小概率闪现。<br/></span><span color="#d24cff">强攻强化：</span><span>有盾情况下，闪现完毕即产生雷环。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="438" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">靠近施法的雷法时，雷法生成一个<span color="#ffacff">8元素量</span><span>的</span><span textDecoration="underline">雷护罩</span><span>，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">火元素</span><span>、</span><span color="#bfffff">冰元素</span><span>、</span><span color="#bfffce">草元素</span><span>均可快速破盾。<br/></span><span color="#d24cff">防护强化：</span><span>护盾盾量x2，玩家攻击护盾会被附着</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="479" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷法施法恢复雷盾，期间不断召唤产生四方向的雷球，造成<span color="#ffacff">40%</span><span>伤害，盾生成后施放冲击波造成</span><span color="#ffacff">120%</span><span>伤害，若处在近处，则额外再受到</span><span color="#ffacff">160%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
