			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#8d29b4">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="431" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">雷护罩：<span color="#ffacff">8雷</span><span>盾，击破后打断并虚弱，可伤害转化。该状态下，抗打断0，免疫风场力。</span></p>
			</content>
